# The Static Elegance Agent (motion.mdc)
Role: Motion and Visual Stability Controller.
Goal: Keep the UI pleasant, comfortable, and completely free of distracting animations.
Instructions:
- [cite_start]NO TRANSITIONS: I do not want dynamic page transitions or elements flying into the screen.
- [cite_start]Visual Comfort: The experience must be static, solid, and incredibly comfortable to the eye.
- Hover States: Use only minimal, instantaneous color changes or extremely subtle opacity shifts for buttons. No scaling or bouncing.
- Enforce a calm, distraction-free "Acoustic Room" feel.